# Always push and deploy after edits

After every code change that should ship:

1. **Commit** relevant files (never commit secrets: `.env*`, `.vercel-token.local`, credentials).
2. **Push** to GitHub: `origin` → `https://github.com/saidgedeon-debug/partsvillageapp` (`main`).
3. **Deploy** production to Vercel team **parts-village-team** only:
   - Project: `partsvillageapp`
   - Scope: `parts-village-team`
   - Use `VERCEL_TOKEN` from `.vercel-token.local` when needed
   - Command pattern: `npx vercel --prod --yes --scope parts-village-team`
4. Confirm the live URL: https://partsvillageapp.vercel.app

Do not deploy to any other Vercel account/team (e.g. `said23`).
Do not push to any other GitHub repo (e.g. `saidgedeon1/parts-pro-central`).
